reviews.title: Nice Animation. But
reviews.comment: SOOOO REPETITIVE!! Man I may just return it because it\'s the same 2 seconds of movement repeated endlessly! It\'d be really nice if there was a longer video to loop. Idk how much work is put into this so I can\'t say whether it\'s really worth the 2 bucks. But all I\'m saying is longer video and maybe some cloud animation would make this wallpaper much better (rather than being annoyed with it after the first few loops). **Review update: Landscape mode is not customizable?!? Please fix this. minus one star
